            FirewallAllowAzureIps = "Enabled",
            FirewallRules =

                {

                    Name = "test_rule",
                    StartIpAddress = "1.1.1.1",
                },
            },
            FirewallState = "Enabled",
            Identity = new AzureNextGen.DataLakeStore.Latest.Inputs.EncryptionIdentityArgs
            {
                Type = "SystemAssigned",

            ResourceGroupName = "contosorg",
            Tags = 
            {
                { "test_key", "test_value" },
            },

            TrustedIdProviders = 
            {

                {

                    Name = "test_trusted_id_provider_name",
                },
            },
        });

}

### Outputs

All [input](#inputs) properties are implicitly available as output properties. Additionally, the Account resource produces the following output properties:




{{% choosable language csharp %}}
<dl class="resources-properties">
